<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="frighten-sb-to-death-frighten-the-life-out-of-sb">frighten sb to death / frighten the life out of sb</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>把某人吓得要命：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Spiders frighten her to death. / Spiders frighten the life out of her.
蜘蛛把她吓得要死。</p></div>

<p>注: frighten用法及意义同scare，但比scare稍正式。  </p></div>